data.description: This home has recently gone through several updates.  Renovated to perfection, this charming home features many updates. Beautiful vinyl plan flooring in high traffic areas and new carpet in all the bedrooms as well as the living room.  Freshly painted inside and out. New roof! This home is located in the highly desireable Almond Tree neighborhood, just a very short distance to the neighborhood recently new elementary school.  This home features a very new and modern water filtration system that also softens the water.  Just put in last year.    The back yard is beautiful with a patio, block fence, sprinkler system and a lush yard during the summer
